title: Secret Men's Business
description: Four former private school boys' reunite to attend the funeral of their beloved but mysterious school master. The weekend of sun, surf, women and late-night reminiscing leads to hard truths that had long been left behind. (1999)
description2: Four former private school boys' reunite to attend the funeral of their beloved but mysterious school master. The weekend of sun, surf, women and late-night reminiscing leads to hard truths that had long been left behind.

title: California Suite
description: Neil Simon's laugh-drenched adaptation of his hit Broadway play, intertwining the misadventures of four groups of guests at the Beverly Hills Hotel. (1978)
description2: Neil Simon's laugh-drenched adaptation of his hit Broadway play, intertwining the misadventures of four groups of guests at the Beverly Hills Hotel.

title: Lucy The Human Chimp
description: Chimpanzee Lucy was raised as a human in a suburban family home where she was taught to communicate. Out of an experiment filled with surprises, a beautiful friendship was born.
description2: Chimpanzee Lucy was raised as a human in a suburban family home where she was taught to communicate. Out of an experiment filled with surprises, a beautiful friendship was born.

title: Jack Irish: Dead Point
description: When a high profile judge commissions Jack Irish to locate a mysterious red book, Jack is thrown into a world of sexy club owners, drug dealers and unhinged killers. (Movie 3 of 3) (2013)

title: Shed
description: An enslaved girl, Mary, endures daily torture in a world with no prospects until a new station hand, Victor, walks into the shed and her life.
